{"tid":1545121,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"關於831事件","createTime":"2019-09-05T20:50:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T05:06:36.000Z","uid":283713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"58a7c0830dc4bfb2f476d3d1fe6df1512dd1e135","tid":1545121,"uid":283713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T20:50:40.000Z","msg":"全世界係得網絡上尋831失蹤既人<br />\n請問可唔可以要求傳媒，立法會議員開聲要求831失蹤既家人提供資料？<br />\n可能當事人未必係示威者，只係純粹經過冇唸過會有呢個結果，冇朋友知道岀左事，家人年老唔識用手機，可唔可以用傳統少少方法例如登報？或貼街招？<br />\n<br />\n我唔知呢個方法蠢唔蠢但我只希望盡量全世界都知！只少我屋企人都係透過我把口同電視先知情況！唔知咩叫連登！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可行的話請幫推！</span></span>"},{"pid":"565ef5f0aaff2e49cb38bdaa17053d8d13870a24","tid":1545121,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T20:50:48.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7bb3ef62a0e84e3b9575082f5691202bcd3305e1","tid":1545121,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T20:51:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wsT945D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwsT945D.jpg&h=1911c235&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84HwjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=7db70be8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"5249c3a8fa598761f66b8ca86702326a344bcbe6","tid":1545121,"uid":283713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":